{
  "page": "Men of the Reach",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:T_Jedruszek_MenOfTheMander.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/T_Jedruszek_MenOfTheMander.jpg/350px-T_Jedruszek_MenOfTheMander.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"292\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/T_Jedruszek_MenOfTheMander.jpg/525px-T_Jedruszek_MenOfTheMander.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e6/T_Jedruszek_MenOfTheMander.jpg/700px-T_Jedruszek_MenOfTheMander.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:T_Jedruszek_MenOfTheMander.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Men of the <a href=\"/index.php/Mander\" title=\"Mander\">Mander</a>, by Tomasz Jedruszek © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Men of the Reach</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> are natives of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, a southern region of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Ethnicity\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Ethnicity</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Culture\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Culture</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Religion\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Religion</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Customs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Customs</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ethnicity\">Ethnicity</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Men_of_the_Reach&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Ethnicity\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Many <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> claimed descent from <a href=\"/index.php/Garth_Greenhand\" title=\"Garth Greenhand\">Garth Greenhand</a>, legendary <a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_First_Men\" title=\"High King of the First Men\">High King of the First Men</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_garth_greenhand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_garth_greenhand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a> were uprooted by the First Men.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_the_gardener_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_the_gardener_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> The various smaller realms of the Reach eventually came under the dominion of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Kings_of_the_Reach\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kings of the Reach\">Kings of the Reach</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Rather than oppose the <a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">coming of the Andals</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sage_Kings\" title=\"Three Sage Kings\">Three Sage Kings</a> welcomed the newcomers to the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, allowing First Men and <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a> to come together peacefully.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_andals_in_the_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_andals_in_the_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Culture\">Culture</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Men_of_the_Reach&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Culture\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Religion\">Religion</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Men_of_the_Reach&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Religion\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dimitri_Bielak_Riches_of_the_Reach.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/Dimitri_Bielak_Riches_of_the_Reach.jpg/350px-Dimitri_Bielak_Riches_of_the_Reach.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"233\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/Dimitri_Bielak_Riches_of_the_Reach.jpg/525px-Dimitri_Bielak_Riches_of_the_Reach.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e6/Dimitri_Bielak_Riches_of_the_Reach.jpg/700px-Dimitri_Bielak_Riches_of_the_Reach.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dimitri_Bielak_Riches_of_the_Reach.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Riches of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, by Dimitri Bielak © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a> is the predominant religion in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, with the new gods having been welcomed by the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sage_Kings\" title=\"Three Sage Kings\">Three Sage Kings</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_andals_in_the_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_andals_in_the_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/Starry_Sept\" title=\"Starry Sept\">Starry Sept</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> was the seat of the <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a> for \"a thousand years prior\" to the <a href=\"/index.php/Wars_of_Conquest\" title=\"Wars of Conquest\">Wars of Conquest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Pate_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Pate-7\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Customs\">Customs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Men_of_the_Reach&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Customs\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The traditions of chivalry and singers are said to have begun in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> where legends claim chivalry was brought by the First Knight, <a href=\"/index.php/John_the_Oak\" title=\"John the Oak\">John the Oak</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_garth_greenhand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_garth_greenhand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Knighthood\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Knighthood\">Knighthood</a> is most esteemed in the Reach compared to the rest of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> and many <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourneys</a> are held in the region.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_highgarden.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_highgarden.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> of the educated <a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\">maesters</a> is found in the ancient city of <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> Some say the <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor\" title=\"Arbor\">Arbor</a> makes the best <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Considered the breadbasket of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>, the Reach has a rich farming culture.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Many men of the Reach consider <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a> to their south to be their ancient enemies.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_iv.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_queer_customs_of_the_south.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_queer_customs_of_the_south.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Noble <a href=\"/index.php/Bastardy\" title=\"Bastardy\">bastards</a> born in the Reach can be given the surname Flowers.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Men_of_the_Reach&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Queen%27s_Retinue_by_Drazenka_Kimpel.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/dd/The_Queen%27s_Retinue_by_Drazenka_Kimpel.jpg/350px-The_Queen%27s_Retinue_by_Drazenka_Kimpel.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"331\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/dd/The_Queen%27s_Retinue_by_Drazenka_Kimpel.jpg/525px-The_Queen%27s_Retinue_by_Drazenka_Kimpel.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/dd/The_Queen%27s_Retinue_by_Drazenka_Kimpel.jpg/700px-The_Queen%27s_Retinue_by_Drazenka_Kimpel.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Queen%27s_Retinue_by_Drazenka_Kimpel.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a> and her retinue, by Drazenka Kimpel © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Once and always a great realm, the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> is many things to its inhabitants: the most populous, fertile, and powerful domain in the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a>, its wealth second only to the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">gold-rich west</a>; a <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">seat of learning</a>; a center of music, culture, and all the arts, bright and dark; the breadbasket of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>; a nexus of trade; a home to great seafarers, wise and noble kings, dread <a href=\"/index.php/Sorcerer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sorcerer\">sorcerers</a>, and the most beautiful women in all Westeros.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;writings of <a href=\"/index.php/Yandel\" title=\"Yandel\">Yandel</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Many noble houses of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> trace their ancestry back to <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> adventurers given lands and wives by <a href=\"/index.php/Garth_IX_Gardener\" title=\"Garth IX Gardener\">Garth IX</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Merle_I_Gardener\" title=\"Merle I Gardener\">Merle I</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Gwayne_V_Gardener\" title=\"Gwayne V Gardener\">Gwayne V</a>, amongst them the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Orme\" title=\"House Orme\">Ormes</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Graceford\" title=\"House Graceford\">Gracefords</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Cuy\" title=\"House Cuy\">Cuys</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Roxton\" title=\"House Roxton\">Roxtons</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Uffering\" title=\"House Uffering\">Ufferings</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Leygood\" title=\"House Leygood\">Leygoods</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Varner\" title=\"House Varner\">Varners</a>. As the centuries passed, the sons and daughters of these houses intermarried so freely with those descended from the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> that it became impossible to tell them apart. Seldom has a conquest been achieved with less bloodshed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_andals_in_the_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_andals_in_the_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;writings of <a href=\"/index.php/Yandel\" title=\"Yandel\">Yandel</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>You need to come south. You need a taste of summer before it flees. In <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a> there are fields of golden <a href=\"/index.php/Rose\" title=\"Rose\">roses</a> that stretch away as far as the eye can see. The fruits are so ripe they explode in your mouth—melons, peaches, <a href=\"/index.php/Fireplum\" title=\"Fireplum\">fireplums</a>, you've never tasted such sweetness.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Men_of_the_Reach&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Pate-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Pate_7-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Pate_(novice)\" title=\"Pate (novice)\">Pate</a> recalls the <a href=\"/index.php/Starry_Sept\" title=\"Starry Sept\">Starry Sept</a> \"had been the seat of the <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a> for a thousand years before <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Landing\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Landing\">Aegon landed</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.\" (<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Prologue\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Prologue\">Prologue</a>). It is unknown if this is an exact figure or if <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> is being figurative.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Men_of_the_Reach&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Aegon's Conquest.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_garth_greenhand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_garth_greenhand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_garth_greenhand.7B.7B.7